46 vector<visualization_msgs::Marker> createTargetMarkers(vector<pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ> > clouds, vector<geometry_msgs::Pose> lasers)
47 {
48 
49  static Markers marker_list;
50  int nLasers=lasers.size();
51 
52  //Reduce the elements status, ADD to REMOVE and REMOVE to delete
53  marker_list.decrement();
54 
55  // Create a colormap
56  class_colormap colormap("hsv",10, 1, false);
57 
58  visualization_msgs::Marker marker_centers;
59  visualization_msgs::Marker marker_lasers[nLasers];
60 
61  marker_centers.header.frame_id = "/my_frame3";
62  marker_centers.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
63 
64  marker_centers.ns = "centers";
65  marker_centers.action = visualization_msgs::Marker::ADD;
66 
67  marker_centers.type = visualization_msgs::Marker::SPHERE_LIST;
68 
69  marker_centers.scale.x = 0.08;
70  marker_centers.scale.y = 0.08;
71  marker_centers.scale.z = 0.08;
72 
73  /*marker_centers.color.b=1;
74  marker_centers.color.a=1;*/
75  marker_lasers[0].color.a=1;
76  marker_lasers[0].color.g=1;
77  marker_lasers[1].color.b=1;
78  marker_lasers[1].color.a=1;
79  marker_lasers[2].color.r=1;
80  marker_lasers[2].color.a=1;
81 
82  for(int n=0; n<clouds.size();n++)
83  {
84  {
85  pcl::PointCloud<pcl::PointXYZ> cloud = clouds[n];
86  std_msgs::ColorRGBA color;
87  color = colormap.color(n);
88 
89  for ( int i = 0; i< cloud.points.size() ; i++)
90  {
91  geometry_msgs::Point pt;
92  pt.x= cloud.points[i].x;
93  pt.y= cloud.points[i].y;
94  pt.z= cloud.points[i].z;
95 
96  marker_centers.points.push_back(pt);
97  marker_centers.colors.push_back(color);
98 
99 
100  } //end for
101  marker_list.update(marker_centers);
102  }
103  }
104 
105  //position and orientation of laser
106  for(int n=0;n<lasers.size();n++)
107  {
108  {
109  marker_lasers[n].header.frame_id = "/my_frame3";
110  marker_lasers[n].header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
111 
112  std::stringstream ss;
113  ss << "Laser " << n;
114 
115  marker_lasers[n].ns = ss.str();
116  marker_lasers[n].action = visualization_msgs::Marker::ADD;
117 
118  marker_lasers[n].type = visualization_msgs::Marker::ARROW;
119 
120  marker_lasers[n].scale.x = 0.2;
121  marker_lasers[n].scale.y = 0.1;
122  marker_lasers[n].scale.z = 0.1;
123 
124  geometry_msgs::Pose laser = lasers[n];
125  std_msgs::ColorRGBA color;
126 
127  color = colormap.color(n);
128 
129  marker_lasers[n].pose.position.x=laser.position.x;
130  marker_lasers[n].pose.position.y=laser.position.y;
131  marker_lasers[n].pose.position.z=laser.position.z;
132 
133  marker_lasers[n].pose.orientation.x=laser.orientation.x;
134  marker_lasers[n].pose.orientation.y=laser.orientation.y;
135  marker_lasers[n].pose.orientation.z=laser.orientation.z;
136  marker_lasers[n].pose.orientation.w=laser.orientation.w;
137 
138  marker_lasers[n].color=color;
139 
140  marker_list.update(marker_lasers[n]);
141  }
142  }
143 
144  //Remove markers that should not be transmitted
145  marker_list.clean();
146 
147  //Clean the marker_vector and put new markers in it;
148  return marker_list.getOutgoingMarkers();
149 
150 } //end function
